description	"Princess Leia Organa

Class: Bounty Hunter.
Class Summary: 
A pistoleer medic (Heals HP) and commander with Force Block and a thermal detonator. 

Weaponry:
- Defender Sporting Pistol (3)
- Thermal Detonator (1)
- Incendiary Grenade (1)

Inventory:
- Bacta (+25 HP)
- Large Bacta (+50 HP)

Forcepowers:
- Sense (3)
- Force Block (2)
- Force Regen 70% slower

Attributes:
- Rally
- Immunity to Mind Trick

Abilities:
- Can recover allies' health [Press the 'Use' key while adjacent and facing teammate with low health]
- Can view ally stats
- Dodge (2) [Class Special 1]
- Flipkick (2)

Leia Organa was a leader in the Alliance to Restore the Republic, a former member of the Imperial Senate, and a member of the Royal Family of Alderaan. She was the biological offspring of the former Jedi Knight Anakin Skywalker and Senator Padme Amidala of Naboo."
